Bayer, Evogene Achieve Milestone in Wheat Genetics Research

-- B y   M a r i a j o s e   V e r a
-- 
2011-09-26T07:06:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/bayer-evogene-achieve-milestone-in-wheat-genetics-research.html
Bayer CropScience AG and  Evogene
Ltd. (EVGN)  reached a milestone in their joint research collaboration
in wheat, the company said in an e-mailed statement today.  Through the use of Evogene’s proprietary tools, more than
200,000 single-nucleotide polymorphisms across the wheat genome
were identified as part of the companies’ efforts to improve
wheat through the application of advanced breeding techniques,
the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mariajose Vera at 
 mvera1@bloomberg.net  